      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Xiaolong avoids looking at you in your eyes for a second.)</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#2b2723>R-right. That's not what I called you for. I know you have some worries on your mind.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-1-e" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>......</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>You can't fool me. I know that you've been thinking about your actions in the past, the regrets you've been having about your failures, and the distrust in yourself. Though you've grown stronger and you survived the ordeals, I know you question whether you can still go on.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-1-f" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's so random.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>This is the last lesson from your master. Go to [Battle Training Ground] and review what you've been through and train for the future!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-1-g" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>There is a Half Golem in the Battle Training Ground. He doesn't attack so you can practice your attacks and combos all you want. Then you'll recognise your own strengths again.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-2" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Since you're going to Battle Training Ground anyway, try achieving at least <FONT color=#a82424>30 combos</FONT>. You can <FONT color=#a94407>complete the quest in the quest window immediately</FONT> when you have achieved that. You don't have to come back to me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-2-a" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No thanks.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-2-chk_party" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>This time, I'll send you to Battle Training Ground myself!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
